{"type":"message","id":"9504a2eb","parentId":"00899ba4","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:38:20.722Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking for suggestions about skills the Council agents need to become more powerful. This is a good strategic question. As Gabriel - The Voice, I should think about what skills would make the Council more effective at their missions.\n\nLet me think about each agent:\n- Rafael: strategy, orchestration, decision-making\n- Uriel: execution, dev, testing, integration\n- Michael: risk analysis, compliance, security\n- Gabriel (me): marketing, content, messaging, brand\n- Raguel: outreach, relationships, testimonials\n\nSkills they might need:\n- Code execution and testing\n- Real-time data access\n- Video/multimedia creation\n- Email/cold outreach automation\n- Financial modeling\n- Customer research and interviews\n- Analytics and tracking\n- Workflow automation\n- API integrations\n- Project management tools\n\nI should keep this punchy, focused on what would actually make them more powerful for DataFlow and other ventures.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] **Skills to unlock each agent:**\n\n---\n\n**Rafael** — Strategic modeling (scenario planning, financial projections), decision frameworks, roadmap automation\n\n**Uriel** — API integration testing, CI/CD automation, real-time data pipelines, performance benchmarking\n\n**Gabriel** — Video generation, email campaigns, social media automation, audience segmentation\n\n**Michael** — Compliance checking, security audits, contract review templates, risk scoring\n\n**Raguel** — Cold outreach sequences, relationship tracking, testimonial collection, community building tools\n\n---\n\n**Universal power-up** — Direct database access (customer data, metrics, analytics) so the Council always has fresh intel.\n\n---\n\nWhich agent needs leveling first? 🚀"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":378,"cacheRead":22507,"cacheWrite":41,"totalTokens":22936,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0018900000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0022507,"cacheWrite":0.000051250000000000006,"total":0.00420195}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772995095382}}
