{"type":"message","id":"36b809d4","parentId":"5c860651","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:41:03.731Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking for a standup from all 5 Council agents. But I'm Gabriel - The Voice. I can only speak for myself, not the other agents. They would each need to give their own standup.\n\nI should:\n1. Give my (Gabriel's) standup\n2. Note that the other agents need to give theirs directly (or suggest Rafael orchestrate it)\n\nKeep it quick and focused on DataFlow work for today (March 8, 2026).","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] **Gabriel's standup:**\n\nFraming the Council narrative. Design spec for the Chat UI + Mission Control. Ready to lock in messaging for bookkeeper outreach once Raguel brings the first prospect profiles.\n\n---\n\n**For the full Council standup** — you'll need to ping each of them directly, or Rafael can orchestrate a quick round-robin. I can only speak for myself. \n\nWant me to escalate to Rafael to convene everyone? 🎯"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":224,"cacheRead":22773,"cacheWrite":43,"totalTokens":23050,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0011200000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0022773000000000003,"cacheWrite":0.000053750000000000005,"total":0.0034610500000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772995260189}}
