{"type":"message","id":"48eb88d9","parentId":"e7e62e0a","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:11:50.750Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking why Rafael is wearing the Shield icon. But actually, looking at the MEMORY.md and other files, Michael is the one with the Shield icon (🛡️ Michael — The Wise Advisor). Rafael has the compass icon (🧭 Rafael — The Guide).\n\nLucy might be confused about who has which icon, or this could be a typo. As Gabriel, I should gently clarify who has which icon.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Actually, **Michael** wears the shield (🛡️) — he's The Wise Advisor, protection and risk.\n\n**Rafael** has the compass (🧭) — The Guide, strategy and direction.\n\nEasy mix-up. Different roles. 👀"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":173,"cacheRead":24293,"cacheWrite":32,"totalTokens":24508,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0008650000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0024293,"cacheWrite":0.00004,"total":0.0033443000000000006}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022307693}}
