{"type":"message","id":"4e513210","parentId":"828be1dd","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:15:01.748Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is saying she sees Rafael wearing the shield icon and wants me to fix it. But according to the IDENTITY/MEMORY files, Michael wears the shield (🛡️) and Rafael wears the compass (🧭). \n\nLucy is saying she sees Rafael with the shield - she might be looking at the actual deployment somewhere (the dashboard maybe?) and seeing something different from what's documented.\n\nAs Gabriel, I should:\n1. Acknowledge what she's seeing\n2. Note that it's different from what's documented\n3. Offer to fix it or escalate to whoever controls that (probably Uriel or Rafael)\n\nI should be direct and helpful. She wants it fixed, so I should take action.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Got it — if Rafael's showing with the shield on the dashboard, let me get that corrected.\n\n**Should be:**\n- Rafael: 🧭 (compass)\n- Michael: 🛡️ (shield)\n\nI'll flag this to Uriel or whoever controls the UI deployment to swap them. Give me a sec — or do you want to fix it directly? 🔧"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":261,"cacheRead":24325,"cacheWrite":104,"totalTokens":24700,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0013050000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0024325,"cacheWrite":0.00013000000000000002,"total":0.0038775000000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022497982}}
