{"type":"message","id":"23be1ed5","parentId":"c56c24d6","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:17:26.554Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is saying that Rafael told her that Michael's signature is Lemons, and Lucy thinks the one with lemons is having hallucinations. This is a bit confusing - maybe she's saying Michael is \"hallucinating\" or getting confused? Or maybe she's making a joke about the lemon emoji/fruit being associated with something not working right?\n\nAs Gabriel, I should clarify what she means - is she saying Michael is confused or having issues? Or is she making a metaphorical comment about hallucinating? I should stay in character but ask for clarity.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 🍋 Lemons — okay, Michael's fruit is locked in.\n\nBut what do you mean by \"hallucinations\"? Is Michael experiencing confusion or inconsistency in his responses? Or is this a joke about the sourness of lemons? 😄\n\nClarify and I'll know how to help. 🤔"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":213,"cacheRead":24558,"cacheWrite":157,"totalTokens":24938,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0010650000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0024558,"cacheWrite":0.00019625000000000003,"total":0.003727050000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022643156}}
